ns, add show() method, fix hide animation (y - 10), use getNextDepth\n4. **UIToa
st** - Complete rewrite using design deliverable\n5. **UIButton** - Add pressedC
olor, killTweensOf, fix fillAlpha recovery\n6. **UIBadge tests** - Add test file
