ssue-19 UIButton** - Add pressedColor, killTweensOf, fix setDisabled param\n9. *
*designs/issue-19 index.ts** - Add unified export\n\nThe approach for production
code:\n- Replace UIPanel.ts with the design deliverable version (with minor adju
stments if needed)\n- Replace UIDialog.ts with the design deliverable version\n-
Replace UIAlert.ts with the design deliverable version  \n- Replace UIToast.ts w
ith the design deliverable version (but need to check if we need backward compat
ibility)\n- Update UIButton.ts\n\nWait, I need to be careful about backward comp
atibility. The review says "保留必要的旧接口兼容性包装" for UIToast. Let me chec
k what the old interface was and what the new one is.\n\nOld UIToast:\n- `ToastT
ype = \'build\' | \'upgrade\' | \'remove\' | \'info\' | \'success\' | \'warning\
'`\n- `UIToastConfig` has `type: ToastType, title: string, message?: string, sta
rtTime?, endTime?, progress?, showProgress?, duration?, onComplete?, onClick?`\n
